title: HenryPorgan
author: HenryPorgan
content: Hello Sirs.  I work in the crypto company now, and I meet new people who work in the cryptosphere, for a joint exchange of knowledge, and possible cooperation.We are engaged in providing payment solutions in India.Now I am looking for new partners for mutually beneficial work.I would like to invite you to work with me. I can tell you everything in more detail if you just let me know.You don't need any investment.If you are interested, please write to me
